The Amazing Digital Circus is not only great with their storytelling, but are also incredible with character building. In today’s episode, I want to take a closer look at two characters that I think may actually be the most relatable characters in the show. Characters who have had to go through their own personal struggles and are figuring how to deal with them even in all the chaos. I also think I have an idea of what’s going to happen next in the show…let’s dive into it!
